column4: The case is just what I expected， I put in my NVMe M.2 SSD into the adapter， plugged it in and started the format. No tools needed and I f you had multiple SSDs you could just swapped. I give it too marks because it did everything I expected it to do. I haven’t tested the speed nor do I have anything to test it with but it seems to be performing as fast as my external SSD.
Excelente， superó mis expectativas. Probado con Samsung SSD 980 1TbSe calienta considerablemente sin afectar el rendimiento， seguiré haciendo pruebas.

column3: works very well. would buy again
